parser
Class XMLParser

java.lang.Object
  parser.XMLParser

public class XMLParser
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to parse out the noun phrases from the XML formatted Review text. The text has been tagged with POS tags using the Stanford Core NLP POS tagger.
